  "Comet Hale-Bopp": "",
  "Comet NEOWISE": "",
  "Halley's Comet": "",
  "Comet Swift-Tuttle": "",
  "The Perseids are caused by debris from Comet Swift-Tuttle, which orbits the Sun every ~133 years.": "",
